---
---

<section id="features" class="bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-50 to-white py-20">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">核心优势</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Feature 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m13.35-.622l1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-2">官方 API 直连</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">非第三方中转，直接对接 Claude、ChatGPT、Cursor 官方接口，原生体验，零延迟。</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Feature 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.623 0-1.602-.397-3.11-1.099-4.499a11.992 11.992 0 00-10.89-3.323z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-2">账号安全保障</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">智能网络优化技术，大幅降低账号异常风险，让你的订阅持久稳定。</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Feature 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
           <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M21 12a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H15a3 3 0 11-6 0H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 12m18 0v6a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 013 18v-6m18 0V9M3 12V9m18 0a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 9m12 3V9m-3 3V9" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-2">人民币直接支付</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">支持微信、支付宝、银行卡，无需虚拟卡或加密货币，国内支付零门槛。</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Feature 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M9 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h3.75c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-2">企业级管理</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">批量开通、成员管理、用量统计、可开国内增值税发票。</p>
      </div>
      <!-- Feature 5 -->
      <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.75 13.5l10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-navy mb-2">极速开通</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">5 分钟完成从注册到订阅的全流程，即买即用。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
